Today the W3C Advisory Committee Representatives received a Proposal to license the SysApps TCP and UDP Socket API specification. Pursuant to the W3C Policy on Relicensing Unfinished W3C Specifications, the Director proposes to relicense the Specification under the W3C Software and Document License. Public comments are welcome through 7 July 2015.<img src="https://www.w3.org/analytics/piwik/piwik.php?idsite=7&amp;rec=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Farchives%2F4746%3Fpk_campaign%3Dfeed%26pk_kwd%3Dcall-for-review-proposal-to-relicense-unfinished-sysapps-specification-tcp-and-udp-socket-api&amp;action_name=Call+for+Review%3A+Proposal+to+Relicense+Unfinished+SysApps+Specification%3A+TCP+and+UDP+Socket+API&amp;urlref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Ffeed" style="border:0;width:0;height:0" width="0" height="0" alt="" />
]]>
</description>
<content:encoded>
<![CDATA[
<p>Today the W3C Advisory Committee Representatives received a <a href="https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-review-announce/2015Jun/0000.html">Proposal to license the SysApps TCP and UDP Socket API specification</a>. Pursuant to the W3C <a href="http://www.w3.org/2014/12/relicense.html">Policy on Relicensing Unfinished W3C Specifications</a>, the Director proposes to relicense the Specification under the <a href="http://www.w3.org/Consortium/Legal/2015/copyright-software-and-document">W3C Software and Document License</a>. Public comments are welcome through <strong>7 July 2015</strong>.</p> <p><img src="https://www.w3.org/analytics/piwik/piwik.php?idsite=7&amp;rec=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Farchives%2F4746%3Fpk_campaign%3Dfeed%26pk_kwd%3Dcall-for-review-proposal-to-relicense-unfinished-sysapps-specification-tcp-and-udp-socket-api&amp;action_name=Call+for+Review%3A+Proposal+to+Relicense+Unfinished+SysApps+Specification%3A+TCP+and+UDP+Socket+API&amp;urlref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Ffeed" style="border:0;width:0;height:0" width="0" height="0" alt="" /></p>
]]>
